{"type": "article", "id": 21048, "title": "可旋转灯罩的台灯", "description": "", "date": "2016-01-21T07:24:29Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 34, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607122313mogkVr1cHqla5LEf.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是巴黎设计师 inga sempé 新推出的灯饰，外形非常普通。里面的灯泡是一个圆球，是由金属杆和底座固定。灯罩反而是脱离的，贴合在球形灯泡上，通过转动灯罩来改变光源的方向。灯罩上的图案是由数字影印而成，根据疏密关系产生渐变的效果。灯光从里面透出来，增加了一层颜色和明暗的渐变，很炫丽。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150729RjJFOU56AMdYCtLp.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"546\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150730D57ZuQk6BJPye0hn.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"546\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150731JgweBhilFdcSv5Ln.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"546\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150732SKrxBcQF3uCfhln7.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"709\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.86674817\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261507326KWNbxIu3MjOoPSd.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"540\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.6601467\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\n\n\n\n"}